              <p class="why-panel-meta"><a href="/cases/neo-mirai">Leia o caso &rarr;</a> &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; <a href="/neo-mirai/">Abra o build ao vivo &rarr;</a></p>
          </article>

          <!-- T5: medium. Brand vs Product registers. -->
